{"tid":2229913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙面法一週年 記唔記得我地點逼支共上絕路？","createTime":"2020-10-04T16:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T03:21:07.000Z","uid":104425,"like":187,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"391f6e5196ce198f2489b4bf345557185bd2df3a","tid":2229913,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcAA3rU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcAA3rU.jpg&h=a554812d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有睇live嘅手足可能會記得<br />\n當晚佈防出奇地少<br />\n近乎放題式任你開花<br />\n點解明知咁多人出<br />\n咁好機會<br />\n唔拉1000幾百個？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5YnJz8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5YnJz8.png&h=0c33622e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為第二日班鳩官死老豆咁嘅樣上電視<br />\n叫市民同暴力割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dRc5Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dRc5Rf.jpg&h=0cc03913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃至十一月中大理大<br />\n港共都係想利用和理非返唔到工<br />\n希望佢地調轉頭屌示威者<br />\n進而喺區選投返俾保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n當然<br />\n因為我地<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">不分化，不割蓆</span></span><br />\n佢地嘅如意算盤打唔響<br />\n區選亦都大敗<br />\n立法會仲天真到以為會35+而取消選舉<br />\n又出黨安法七傷拳<br />\n加上武肺<br />\n形成天下圍中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係時候諗返我地嘅初心<br />\n當我地花咁多時間討論david呢條attention seeker<br />\n<span class=\"red\">可唔可以用返更多時間關注十二手足；旁聽，寫信為本地手足添溫暖</span><br />\n當我地鬧人食黃店當抗爭<br />\n<span class=\"red\">請撫心自問你又有做過啲咩更有價值嘅抗爭行動</span><br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"x-small\">（當然我覺得食黃店係基本，純粹消費選擇，根本唔係抗爭）<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6cf3G6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6cf3G6.jpg&h=31f03c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n選擇自己認同嘅戰線，然後盡力做到最好"},{"pid":"782794484c81d5e0bf3661e1d79db2b4fee083d7","tid":2229913,"uid":338885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:25:23.000Z","msg":"蒙面無罪 立法無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6b93f109abbd7f3e530b95e7ba4a35b629e498","tid":2229913,"uid":104425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"782794484c81d5e0bf3661e1d79db2b4fee083d7","tid":2229913,"uid":338885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:25:23.000Z","msg":"蒙面無罪 立法無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"市民蒙面 林鄭蒙心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c16911c8b2acb72e3973a56b0889aac61e1a76","tid":2229913,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"20279532eb79de7acac37e3e40061c403383b89f","tid":2229913,"uid":39258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18b55a83aa686e6f69bc32ad0cff3da15cdce36a","tid":2229913,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"依家唔蒙面要罰兩千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde790bd62cea0c9b458a9096d65a12fc66ff243","tid":2229913,"uid":94982,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"當時狗有扮示威者破壞港鐵同列車,又要商場提早關閉<br />\n營做宵禁氣氛"},{"pid":"3cdea748127ed859b6e42280e51f2d8844dd5dd4","tid":2229913,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20279532eb79de7acac37e3e40061c403383b89f","tid":2229913,"uid":39258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"like呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f278a744337af4638274ea42190ce327c170e23","tid":2229913,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cdea7481